{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "7.0",
      "line_index": 7,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9ed6b5b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強い日差し、きらめく海。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "9.0",
      "line_index": 9,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e8b70558",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふぅぅ……あ、暑い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "11.0",
      "line_index": 11,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b1f96432",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "熱せられた砂を感じながら{G_PlayerName}は空を見上げて呟いた。するとそこに元気な声が飛んでくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.1",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "86c8217b",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃーんっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4039a614",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そう言って駆け寄ってきたのは水着姿のスゥだった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.1",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1cf918cc",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "やっと来た～！　待ってたんだからねっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9f9a57e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "砂を蹴りながら一直線に走ってきたスゥは、そのままの勢いで{G_PlayerName}に抱きつくと、嬉しそうな顔で見上げてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "41b80bda",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その仕草や抱きつかれた時の柔らかな感触に{G_PlayerName}はドキドキしてしまった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.1",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c4f6d1e",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ほら見て！　スゥのお城！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f7c5413",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お城？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1e38c53",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥの指さすほうに目をやると、そこには大きな砂のお城があった。少々崩れてはいるが、一生懸命作ったことがよくわかる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ca35fc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "すごいじゃないか、これスゥが一人で作ったのかい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ea8ee7c7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな{G_PlayerName}の問いかけに、スゥは照れくさそうに笑いながら呟いた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.1",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "de2dc34d",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "一人で作ったけどさ……やっぱりお兄ちゃんと一緒がいいの",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2b9c9730",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "スゥ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.1",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "32784cde",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ねえお兄ちゃん、こっちこっち♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.0",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59e1a0ff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥはそう言うと{G_PlayerName}の手を取り引っ張っていく。その仕草には大好きな人と一緒にいられる喜びがまっすぐに表れていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.1",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "700df0e4",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃん、二人のお城作ろう♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9aff384e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、いいよ、作ろうか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.1",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d96f027e",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "わーい♪　スゥはお砂を集めておくから、お兄ちゃんお水持ってきて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6d44fc48",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "オッケー",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "554d339d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二人は分担しながら砂のお城を作り、楽しい時間を過ごす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.0",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b3cdc9df",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥは終始楽しそうにしていて、{G_PlayerName}のそばから離れようとしなかった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.1",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "575fd167",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ね、いい感じでしょ？　やっぱりお兄ちゃんとだと違うね♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.0",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "67f713e1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "できあがった砂のお城を見つめながらスゥは満足そうに微笑む。そんなスゥを見て{G_PlayerName}はほんわかとした気持ちになっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "417d52e6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "砂のお城ができた後、二人は波打ち際へと移動して水遊びを始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.1",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5f3917e4",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃん、そ～れ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1b6cfae",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スゥははしゃぎながら{G_PlayerName}に水をばしゃばしゃとかけてきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c0cce18f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うわっ！　やったな～",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.1",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c7be9a85",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "えへへ♪　冷たかった？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "83f86f1a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それじゃあお返しだ！　えいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.1",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c87151d4",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "きゃあっ！　つめた～い♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ccc693b4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そのまま波打ち際でスゥと{G_PlayerName}は水遊びを楽しむと、少し休憩するために移動を始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2efb89a3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "するとスゥは{G_PlayerName}の腕にしがみつき、体をぴったりと寄せて言った。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.1",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "746ec04a",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃん、もっと遊ぼ？　まだ遊び足りないよ～",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2bc41bce",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そこまで言ってふとスゥは{G_PlayerName}のほうへと目を向ける。{G_PlayerName}はスゥではなく別のほうに目を向けていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e91927ad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それに気づいたスゥは{G_PlayerName}の顔を覗き込んでくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8c5d3f7",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "……ねえ、お兄ちゃん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f08f18a2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……ん？　どうした、スゥ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.1",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "259b4334",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "ちゃんとスゥのこと見ててよ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1fba3969",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あっ……ごめんごめん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4e6dad4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな指摘を受けた{G_PlayerName}はまっすぐスゥの顔に自らの顔を見た。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f4d662cd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すると膨れっ面だったスゥの顔がふっと緩んで笑みを浮かべる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.1",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "abd0d1d9",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "まあいいけどさ……スゥが一番なら許してあげる",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eccd579",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}はスゥの言葉に恥ずかしそうな笑みを浮かべると、その小さな手を取り遊びへと戻っていった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.0",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "23a162d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぎゅっと握り返すスゥの手は強すぎず、けれどしっかりとした「独占したい」という気持ちが感じられる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.1",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9433989f",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃん、いっぱい遊んだね……楽しかった♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "63cd70e0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夕焼けに染まる砂浜、遊び疲れたスゥは{G_PlayerName}の隣へと腰を下ろして肩に寄りかかりながら呟いた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.0",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3c4fd89f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "昼間の元気な感じは少し落ち着き、穏やかな空気が流れていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fd48657e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな中、スゥは隣に座っている{G_PlayerName}の手をそっと握りながら言った。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.1",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "eac84792",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "お兄ちゃんと一緒だとさ、なんか安心するの……だから……また来ようね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "690c0b07",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "上目遣いで見つめてくるスゥを見て、{G_PlayerName}は少し頬を赤く染める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.1",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e3f9c31c",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "スゥ、お兄ちゃんと一緒に過ごすこういう時間、もっと欲しいなって思ってるの",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f61556a1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それは決して強く束縛するわけでもなく、ただ素直な願いとして口にした言葉。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.0",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ed8cb7c1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そっか……それじゃあもっと、こういう時間を作ろうな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf798388",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}の言葉にスゥは嬉しそうな笑みを浮かべ、そのまま軽く肩に頭を預けて目を細めた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.1",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "93fdde37",
      "speaker": "スゥ",
      "ja": "約束だよ……お兄ちゃん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.0",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e2da2c25",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ、約束だ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21395075",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夕焼けの中、波の音に包まれながら――。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "98784a1f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二人の時間は、優しく続いていくのだった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
